<paragraph blockId="7.[192,1440,1313,1373]" pageId="7" pageNumber="6">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,276,1313,1339]" pageId="7" pageNumber="6">Habits.</emphasis>
Apparently attracted to excrement: 
<specimenCount box="[677,830,1313,1339]" pageId="7" pageNumber="6" type="generic">one specimen</specimenCount>
examined was labelled “oak-madroño-pine woodland, at dung trap (human),” and another “cow dung.”
</paragraph>
